entry.value: select tpep_pickup_datetime, tpep_dropoff_datetime, passenger_count, DOLocationID, payment_type, fare_amount from FLOWFILE where tpep_pickup_datetime BETWEEN '2021-12-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-02-28 23:59:59' AND tpep_dropoff_datetime BETWEEN '2021-12-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-02-28 23:59:59' AND tpep_pickup_datetime IS NOT NULL AND tpep_dropoff_datetime IS NOT NULL AND passenger_count IS NOT NULL AND DOLocationID IS NOT NULL AND payment_type IS NOT NULL AND fare_amount IS NOT NULL
